snippet.textDisplay:
Bismillah...Bismillah....Bismillah...
Bismillah ur-Rahman ir-Rahim

Bismillah....Bismillah....
ur-Rahman ir Rahim

Maula tu Rahim
Maula tu Karim

Barqaton ka paigham mile
Kehne se:
La Ilaha illalah
Rehmaton ka salaam mile
Bas kehne se Bismillah...
Bismillah.Bismillah.Bismillah.Bismillah

Tere naam se shuru hua
Tere naam pe khatam lillah
Bismillah....aaaa
Bismillah....aaaa

Mushqilein aasaan hui
Saari aafat tal gayi
Ho Allah...Allah..Allah..Allah

Naimate naazil hui
Marti khwahish pal gayi
Teri mill jaaye panaah
Mere kehne se bus Bismillah
Bismillah....aaaa

Dua jis cheez ki keejie
Toh bas Allah se keejie
Dua jis cheez ki keejie
Toh bas Allah se keejie
Shuru jis kaam ko keejie
Toh Bismillah se keejie
Dua...Dua...Dua..

Dua jis cheej ki keejie
Toh bas Allah se keejie
Dua..Dua..jis cheez ki keejie
Toh bas Allah se keejie
Shuru jis kaam ko keejie
Toh Bismillah se keejie
Bismillah...Bismillah..aaaa

Tere naam se shuru huaa
Tere naam pe khatam lillah
Bismillah...Sa re ma pa ni
Bismillah...

Kuch hidaayat kuch karam
Kuch inaayat kuch reham
Oh Allah, Allah...
Kuch hidaayat kuch karam
Kuch inaayat kuch reham

Thodi hain farmaaishein
Jo ho zara gunjaaishein
Naa koi majboor ho
Barsa de jo tu noor to
Iss lifaafe pe likha
Iss lifaafe pe likha hai
Dil se maine Bismillah
Bismillah...aaaa
Bismillah...aaaa

Tere naam se shuru hua
Tere naam pe khatam lillah
Bismillah...oooo
Bismillah...aaaa
Bismillah...Bismillah...Bismillah..


Peace. Love to all. 💙💜
